reviews.name: Six Star Pro Nutrition Fit French Vanilla Lean Protein, 1.2 lbs
reviews.reviewText: I was shocked to taste this protein powder after reading the great "tasting" reviews on it. It not only tastes disgusting with a medicine flavor, it doesn't mix well either. After 5 minutes of shaking in my blender bottle, there was still clumps in it. I even tried it in a smoothie with banana and strawberries and the horrible medicine taste is still very strong. I'm not a typical protein powder fan, but I can tolerate the EAS brand. This one is just disgusting!
reviews.title: Can't get it down

reviews.name: Six Star Pro Nutrition Fit French Vanilla Lean Protein, 1.2 lbs
reviews.reviewText: bought the French vanilla flavor and tastes horrible. Mixed it into my morning smoothie with fruit and milk. Had to dump it out it. Will return it to the store and buy a different brand. YUCK!!!!!!!

reviews.reviewText: my wife is in LOVE with this protein, she always wanted a "more women specific" protein. she likes the way it tastes, mixes. i actually really like the flavor as well. but the ingredients are on point. mixes easy w any kind of milk or water.
